### Retrieve Attachments

This endpoint retrieves a list of attachments based on the specified query parameters.

#### Request

- Method: GET
- URL: `{{common_api_url}}/appointments/attachments`
- Query Parameters:
    - `per_page` (optional): Specifies the number of attachments per page.
    - `setter_ids` (optional): Comma-separated list of setter IDs.
    - `from_date` (optional): Start date for filtering attachments.
    - `to_date` (optional): End date for filtering attachments.
    - `customer_ids` (optional): Comma-separated list of customer IDs.
    - `closer_ids` (optional): Comma-separated list of closer IDs.
    - `status_ids` (optional): Comma-separated list of status IDs.

#### Response (JSON Schema)

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "current_page": { "type": "integer" },
    "data": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": { "type": "integer" },
          "attachmentUrl": { "type": "string" },
          "type": { "type": "string" },
          "userId": { "type": "integer" },
          "appointmentId": { "type": "integer" }
        }
      }
    },
    "first_page_url": { "type": "string" },
    "from": { "type": "integer" },
    "last_page": { "type": "integer" },
    "last_page_url": { "type": "string" },
    "links": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "url": { "type": "string" },
          "label": { "type": "string" },
          "active": { "type": "boolean" }
        }
      }
    },
    "next_page_url": { "type": "string" },
    "path": { "type": "string" },
    "per_page": { "type": "integer" },
    "prev_page_url": { "type": "string" },
